{"id": 1877, "genre": 1001, "title": "信息爆炸时代，你觉得哪些事反而让人变得更加闭塞？", "description": "那些给得越多反而得到越少的事都是怎么发生的。(题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 5115, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170829100134XVamUfzgpy7rEbtN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-30T03:00:54Z", "options": [{"id": 232705, "content": "容易被媒体左右了言论 限制了思考的维度", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119708}, {"id": 232707, "content": "心与心的交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910599}, {"id": 232708, "content": "只关注自己关注的内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118055}, {"id": 232709, "content": "其实很多真正需要的知识你很难找到", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119718}, {"id": 232710, "content": "随波逐流", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475848}, {"id": 232711, "content": "死宅，没有眼见为实", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988733}, {"id": 233479, "content": "什么都想知道，但什么都没记住", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122233}, {"id": 232713, "content": "各种禁评", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088006}, {"id": 232714, "content": "道德绑架？喷子？键盘侠？段子手？归根结底，还是网友的素质问题，亦或者他们认识不到这是个问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119736}, {"id": 232715, "content": "只求量，缺乏质的正能量新闻，无形中将暴力，消极，不公的思想价值观传播开来。太易扭曲纯洁的心灵，直至某些社会的不良风气。虽然我是90后，表示现在只关注像好奇心日报，央视新闻，财经类的趣味，正能量新闻。对娱乐新闻嗤之以鼻，表示反感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102377}, {"id": 232716, "content": "被逼格刺激的网络生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 232717, "content": "相爱没有那么容易，每个人有他的手机！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941259}, {"id": 232718, "content": "信息爆炸的是零碎化信息\n人们对事情片面且自认为了解很多", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845787}, {"id": 233230, "content": "宅在家里", "image": "img/option/option/20170901124935CrPv48eyKboqSO0R", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121412}, {"id": 233486, "content": "标题和内容完全没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122294}, {"id": 232719, "content": "非正确的观点被扭曲为正常范畴，这种情况成增长趋势，客观公正的论证变得模糊。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119754}, {"id": 232720, "content": "新闻频道放出来的都是什么东西？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897571}, {"id": 234514, "content": "大师级看十年前看武侠看鸿观，晓说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090680}, {"id": 234515, "content": "看大师级作品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090680}, {"id": 234516, "content": "呼唤大师\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090680}, {"id": 232725, "content": "社交违背本质", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793207}, {"id": 234517, "content": "呼唤大师", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1090680}, {"id": 232726, "content": "在空间或者朋友圈，一个段子每隔几个月就会看见一次，而且图片也会一遍又一遍的传，直到模糊不堪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118359}, {"id": 232727, "content": "語言貧乏無力，網絡用語泛濫，使思想變得狹隘", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116278}, {"id": 232216, "content": "信息源内容同质化，喜好算法让推送机构只推送读者乐意点开的内容", "image": null, "praise_count": 724, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 232728, "content": "不知道哪些是假的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112615}, {"id": 232217, "content": "讲究实效，观点不合的网友/朋友拉黑删除屏蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 232729, "content": "大脑天然喜欢偷懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119821}, {"id": 232218, "content": "段子式表述泛滥，严肃命题被忽视或儿戏对待", "image": null, "praise_count": 879, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 232730, "content": "手机手机手机手机手机互联网互联网互联网互联网互联网", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991408}, {"id": 232731, "content": "很多人刚刚因为稍有见解的知识因优越感而难以与他人理性讨论，闭塞在一定程度上发生了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119734}, {"id": 232987, "content": "天天低头看手机，还不够闭塞么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097506}, {"id": 233499, "content": "所学的专业知识和词汇被大家熟知，本以为很好，换来的却是人们的不以为然和断章取义的借口", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057904}, {"id": 232732, "content": "手机电脑代替了亲人爱人成为最重要的“人”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119835}, {"id": 233756, "content": "道德评判变成评判是非曲直的最高标准，不就事论事，非要千方百计挖掘受害人的“污点”，批判一番。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124304}, {"id": 232733, "content": "同质化、假通俗化、无休止的情绪调动、无休止的底线突破", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765559}, {"id": 232478, "content": "无良媒体和标题党故意带节奏，做不出客观的报道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 433, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1111379}, {"id": 233758, "content": "过度的娱乐化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124423}, {"id": 232479, "content": "键盘侠横行，一个热点事件出来下面就一堆莫名其妙的喷子，客观理性的分析已经越来越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 585, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283499}, {"id": 232480, "content": "各种标题党和评论下的喷子五毛，成功帮我戒掉了看新闻的习惯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1109854}, {"id": 232736, "content": "自嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906244}, {"id": 232992, "content": "旁收杂览，浅尝辄止", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031025}, {"id": 233760, "content": "丧失自我分析能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539955}, {"id": 232481, "content": "震惊！男默女泪！", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080118}, {"id": 232737, "content": "渣浪的开放性一年不如一年", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043839}, {"id": 232482, "content": "以为手机就是一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 562962}, {"id": 232738, "content": "过滤式阅读，断章取义，让人丧失了思考。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119900}, {"id": 232483, "content": "微博营销号扎堆似的转发，完全不加思考。", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763873}, {"id": 232739, "content": "老妈会走过来信誓旦旦的和你说，从今以后这个不能吃那个不能吃，都有毒；哪个明星去世了呀；我教你个办法怎么减肥，晚上吃蜂蜜加火龙果……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1119910}, {"id": 232484, "content": "舆论集体主义，强迫站队与虚伪的道德绑架。总喜欢站在道德制高点上指手划脚、大众点评他人的价值与生活，不冷么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 317, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106197}]}